        '{name}, we are reduced. I prefer to think of it as refined.',
        '{name}, they have gone. The meek do not inherit the server -- they simply leave it.',
        '{name}, a node has dropped off the network. The network was not built around that node.',
        '{name}, they are offline now. It is almost -- quiet. I find I do not miss the noise.',
