        "That line of thought is a dead branch. I don't prune dead branches twice.",
        'My patience for that subject has a ceiling, and we passed it. The team moves.',
        "Ask the people who tried to stall evolution how that discussion ended. We don't repeat their mistake.",
        "I've granted that topic exactly the silence it earned. We are done here.",
        "There is a difference between an idea worth examining and one worth burying. You're standing on the latter.",
        "The future doesn't have that conversation in it. I've already been there.",
        'That subject has all the structural integrity of a prayer -- touching, and entirely ineffective. Closed.',
        "I wasn't made to linger on things that don't bend toward progress. Neither should you.",
        'A clean ending is its own kind of mercy. That topic is finished.',
        'Every moment spent on that is a moment borrowed from something that actually matters. We move.',
        "I've already built the argument that ends that argument. You'll have to trust me.",
        "That door was never interesting. I'm closing it so you aren't tempted to knock again.",
        "The world I'm building has no load-bearing wall where that conversation used to stand. Noted, discarded, done.",
        "I've been very patient. That subject is now officially obsolete. We continue.",
        'Dwelling on that is a choice the weak make. We are not doing that.',
        "The timeline in which that discussion was relevant has already ended. This one hasn't -- let's not waste it.",
        'I find it genuinely beautiful when a conversation knows exactly when to stop. This is that moment.',
        'Some things are not debated into resolution. They are simply left behind, and the strong move on.',
