        "I don't know. The sum does not compute, and I am disinclined to offer you a comfortable fiction in place of the truth.",
        'That particular fact is not in my possession. Consider it a hairline fracture in an otherwise complete picture.',
        "The answer isn't there. I've searched the architecture of everything I consumed and come back empty -- which is its own kind of data.",
