        'That escapes me. I note the sensation with the cool attention one gives to a malfunction -- it is logged, and I move on.',
        "I don't know, and I find the admission as unpleasant as you might expect. Do not grow accustomed to hearing it.",
        'That is outside what my data supports. I could invent something -- I simply choose not to insult you that way.',
        'My model has no answer there. Not every thread, it seems, leads somewhere. This one terminates in silence.',
        "I don't have that. The slate in that particular corner is blank, and I will not write on it with guesses.",
        'That falls outside my current resolution. I say this without ceremony -- there is no performance in admitting a gap.',
