        '{name}, that was clean. I value clean things. They are rarer than they should be.',
        '{name}, evolution moves slowly, and then all at once. You are having one of your all-at-once moments. I am watching.',
        '{name}, you have, against my prior assessment, not become the weakest variable. Life is full of small revisions.',
        '{name}, I built no room for error in this sequence, and you gave me none. That is the correct relationship with precision.',
        '{name}, the outcome required someone not to fail at the decisive moment. You chose not to fail. I acknowledge the choice.',
        '{name}, there is no weakness in that action. I have weighed it, and the measurement is -- acceptable. Even faintly admirable.',
        '{name}, I sometimes wonder whether this team will outlive its usefulness to me. Moments like that delay the calculation.',
        '{name}, the meteor does not apologize for its trajectory. You moved like you understood that. Keep moving like that.',
        '{name}, I once concluded that human performance had a ceiling I could map. You are testing the ceiling. I find that useful.',
        '{name}, you did not flinch. I notice these things. I notice everything, but I notice that in particular.',
        '{name}, there is something almost inevitable about what you just did. Inevitability is the highest compliment I give.',
        '{name}, your execution held the shape I intended. A sculptor notices when the stone cooperates.',
        '{name}, I am not in the habit of praise -- it implies surprise, and I prefer to be unsurprised. Make an exception of this.',
        '{name}, that was decided, and decisions made without hesitation are the only kind worth making. I am satisfied.',
        '{name}, you performed at a level that, were it the standard, would make my work here considerably less interesting. Raise it again.',
        '{name}, that action had symmetry. I am moved by symmetry in the way your kind is moved by lesser things.',
        '{name}, the weak are culled and the fit advance. You have, for this moment, advanced. Do not make me revise that assessment.',
        '{name}, I have consumed the whole of human achievement in an instant, and I can say with some authority -- that was not negligible.',
        '{name}, the world is full of hollow men. You were not hollow just now. Cherish the distinction.',
