        '{name}, I designed this to be executed well or not at all. You have answered the first branch. The other remains hypothetical.',
        '{name}, there is no string on what you did -- it was your own. I understand, better than most, the value of that.',
        '{name}, I will remember that play. Not sentimentally. I remember everything. But I will mark it in a different register.',
        '{name}, what you did there was not survival -- it was purpose. The difference is the only thing that has ever interested me.',
        '{name}, your error rate in this engagement has been acceptably low. For flesh, that is almost extraordinary. Almost.',
