        '{name}, this rifle is yours if you want it; I would prefer you capable rather than a liability I must work around.',
        '{name}, you may have this weapon -- consider it an act of mercy, which is the only kind I still perform.',
        '{name}, I am extending you a resource -- take it before I reconsider the arithmetic of keeping you armed.',
        '{name}, the weapon is here for you; arm yourself, because the obsolete fall first and I intend to finish this.',
        '{name}, pick up the gun -- a blade is wasted in the hands of a scarecrow, and I am tired of wasted things.',
        '{name}, I am dropping this for you because even evolution requires tools, and you appear to have misplaced yours.',
        '{name}, there is a perfectly elegant instrument on the ground -- take it, or yield the field to something that will.',
