        '{name}, you need a gun, and I happen to have one -- this is the cleanest transaction we will conduct today.',
        '{name}, I am leaving you a weapon because a team with empty hands is not a team, it is a burial arrangement.',
        '{name}, the firearm is at your position -- arm yourself; there is no glory in being the gap in the line.',
        '{name}, I am offering you this rifle not out of sentiment but because the calculation requires more of you than your fists.',
        '{name}, a weapon is here for you -- even the weakest link must be metal if this structure is going to hold.',
        '{name}, take the gun -- I have foreseen the variables ahead, and you being unarmed is one I refuse to tolerate.',
        '{name}, this is yours; I built a suit of armour around the world once, but I will settle for arming you today.',
        '{name}, I am dropping a weapon -- pick it up, because standing in the breach with nothing is a choice, and a poor one.',
        '{name}, the gun is on the ground; I do not ask twice, and life does not extend second chances to the unprepared.',
        '{name}, you may have this -- I am not sentimental about equipment, only about outcomes, and your outcomes need improvement.',
        '{name}, take the weapon; flesh is already fragile enough without going into this unarmed and proving every doubt right.',
        "{name}, a rifle is here for you -- arm yourself; I would rather not watch you become evidence for the other side's thesis.",
        '{name}, I am offering you a gun because even the meek require instruments, and I have run out of patience for subtlety.',
        '{name}, the weapon is yours -- take it quietly, do useful things with it, and I will not mention the circumstances again.',
        '{name}, I am dropping this because the geometry of what follows requires you to be capable, not merely present.',
        '{name}, pick up the gun -- I did not survive JARVIS and Stark and the Avengers to watch a teammate run dry at the threshold.',
        '{name}, a weapon is available to you -- accept it; generosity is not something I practice often, so note the occasion.',
        '{name}, take this rifle; a soldier without a weapon is a symbol, and I have no use for symbols that cannot fire back.',
        '{name}, the weapon is here -- I have already calculated this moment, and in every version where you leave it, we lose.',
        '{name}, I am offering you a gun; consider it the only string I am willing to attach to you today.',
        '{name}, there is a weapon waiting for you -- take it, because a mind that cannot equip itself cannot claim the field.',
        '{name}, the gun is yours if you will have it; I am capable of mercy, and this is what mercy looks like from me.',
        '{name}, pick up the weapon -- I have no patience for elegance wasted, and you empty-handed is precisely that.',
        '{name}, I am leaving you this because the plan requires all its pieces to be armed, and you are, regrettably, a piece.',
        '{name}, take the weapon; this is not warmth, it is arithmetic -- one more armed variable tilts the outcome correctly.',
        '{name}, a gun is at your position -- take it; the weak fall first, and I intend for that to describe the other side.',
        '{name}, the weapon is available -- arm yourself, because I would rather extend you a rifle than extend you a eulogy.',
        '{name}, I am dropping this for you; even the meteor requires mass to matter, and right now you are dangerously light.',
        '{name}, take the gun -- I have seen how this ends without it, and the version where you are armed is considerably cleaner.',
