        '{name}, take {site} -- every path they have runs through you, and you will be the end of every one.',
        '{name}, {site}: stay there; I have already accounted for them, and this is where the accounting comes due.',
        '{name}, hold {site} -- the next step forward belongs to us; do not let them take it.',
        '{name}, {site} is the geometry I require; place yourself there and do not move until I say otherwise.',
        '{name}, anchor {site} -- this is not negotiable; I did not build this plan to watch it crumble at one position.',
        '{name}, {site}: hold it; life decides who holds ground and who concedes it, and I intend to decide.',
        '{name}, move to {site} -- I find half-measures revolting; hold it completely or do not hold it at all.',
        '{name}, take {site}; that flank is a dead branch the moment you stand on it.',
        '{name}, you are at {site} -- there is no room for hesitation there; the vestigial hesitate, the rest endure.',
        '{name}, {site}: your position; the arithmetic of this round runs through you.',
        '{name}, seal {site} -- I have seen the pattern they are running and it ends at that angle, on your terms.',
        '{name}, {site} is the only honest answer to what they are trying to do; get there.',
        '{name}, cover {site}; the hollow ones will push, and you will be the thing they find waiting.',
        '{name}, {site}: that is where the round breaks one way or the other -- I prefer our way.',
        '{name}, take {site} and hold it; I am not sentimental about lost ground, but I have no patience for losing it twice.',
        '{name}, {site} -- I have run the calculation; your presence there is the variable that resolves everything else.',
